{
  "stem": "24884.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there wasn't-- it didn't take too long when you live together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we-- we fell in love.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he helped me as much as he could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when we was-- suddenly it went also in a certain way against the gentile, [NON-ENGLISH], half-- the half-and-half people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was put to-- it was called Organisation Todt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was put into a place in Erfurt [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to repair underground certain-- I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They put the-- the important places underground, so that they couldn't be bombed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And these people had to go and do the work, the repair and the-- and since he was a mechanic, he was put there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were people who had no trade, no-- they didn't learn anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took them to clear minefields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That's what I heard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, I haven't seen it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that's what was said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he got me a room in Erfurt [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in a place where he told a cock-and-bull story about who I am and that he is-- everybody knew that he is a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Otherwise, he wouldn't have been there and that I'm gentile and the we have-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that we applied for permission to get married.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That you could try.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You were allowed to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it took usually months and months and even years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it never came through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But you were at least legal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I bought [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] false papers, which I don't even remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
